©TAMARA AKOPIAN
SPENT MANY QUEIT[SIC] MOMENTS SITTING HERE
DONATED BY HER DAUGHTER NELLY AND MANY
FRIENDS IN PIMLICO IN HONOUR OF HER UNIQUE
SPIRIT OF LOVE AND BEAUTY"ģ
ęFor Peter Drew OBE (1927-2007)
who created this extension to the Jubilee Walkway
placed here in his memory
by the Trustees of the Jubilee Walkway Trust
JUBILEE WALKWAY"Ī
ģTo Baby Angelina
Our Beautiful angel, Our hearts are filled with sorrow for having left us so soon
We love you; Miss you every moment of everyday
Mum. Dad. Sister & Family"∑
īVERA & STAN GRAHAM
B 1907  D 1991/7
EACH IS GIVEN A BAG OF TOOLS
A SHAPELESS MASS, A BOOK OF RULES
AND EACH MUST MAKE ERE LIFE IS FLOWN
A STUMBLING-BLOCK OR A. STEPPING-STONE."ł
